### PackDMS API — Complete Workflow
### This file demonstrates the full document lifecycle:
### create → upload → activate → update → version → legal hold → retention →
### archive → restore → soft delete → restore → purge, plus ACL and audit.

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 1 — Create a Document Shell (draft)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Employee Contract - John Doe",
  "metadata": {
    "contract_id": "CON-2026-001",
    "department": "HR",
    "type": "employment_agreement"
  }
}

> {%
 client.global.set("document_id", response.body.id);
 %}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 2 — Upload the first version (v1)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract_v1.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample_contract.pdf
--boundary--

> {%
 client.global.set("version_id_v1", response.body.id);
 %}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 3 — Get document details (should show draft + version v1)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 4 — Activate the document (draft → active)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "status": "active"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 5 — Patch document metadata
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
PATCH http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "metadata": {
    "contract_id": "CON-2026-001",
    "department": "HR",
    "type": "employment_agreement",
    "signed": true
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 6 — Upload a second version (v2) — supersedes v1
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract_v2_signed.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample_contract.pdf
--boundary--

> {%
 client.global.set("version_id_v2", response.body.id);
 %}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 7 — List all versions (v1 superseded, v2 active)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 8 — Download version v1
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions/{{version_id_v1}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 9 — Download current version (v2)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions/{{version_id_v2}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 10 — List documents (no filter)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 10b — Search documents by metadata (single field)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents?q={"department":"HR"}&limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 10c — Search documents by metadata (multiple fields)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents?q={"department":"HR","signed":true}&limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 11 — Set Legal Hold on the document
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/legal-hold
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "hold": true,
  "reason": "Ongoing litigation — case REF-2026-4521"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 12 — Verify legal hold is active on the document
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 13 — Set Retention policy on the document
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/retention
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "retain_until": "2030-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 14 — Try to delete the document (should be blocked by legal hold)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "status": "deleted"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 15 — Remove Legal Hold
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/legal-hold
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "hold": false,
  "reason": "Litigation resolved — case REF-2026-4521 closed"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 16 — Clear Retention (set to past date)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/retention
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "retain_until": "2020-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 17 — Archive the document (active → archived)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "status": "archived"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 18 — Restore from archive (archived → active)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/restore
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 19 — Soft-delete the document (active → deleted)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "status": "deleted"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 20 — Restore from soft-delete (deleted → active)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/restore
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 21 — Delete a specific version (v1)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
DELETE http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/versions/{{version_id_v1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 22 — Get ACL rules for the document
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/acl
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 23 — Update ACL rules
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
PUT http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/acl
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

[
  {
    "document_id": "{{document_id}}",
    "grantee_type": "user",
    "grantee_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "permission": "read",
    "created_at": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z"
  },
  {
    "document_id": "{{document_id}}",
    "grantee_type": "user",
    "grantee_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
    "permission": "write",
    "created_at": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z"
  }
]

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 24 — View audit logs (Admin only)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GET http://{{host}}/audit?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STEP 25 — Final soft-delete before ending the workflow
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://{{host}}/documents/{{document_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "status": "deleted"
}
